cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.HC 

The paper discusses the use of Recurrent Neural Networks and skip-gram models for personalized course guidance, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of these models for information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL), as well as the development of a user interface (cs.HC) and the deployment of the system at a university (cs.CY).
